channel.description:
This is not a completly blank source and i was not aiming for htat i was aiming to take out the info like Welcome to figmentscape and add welcome to [your server name here] And i added a custom admin + zone and new home zone. Please dont flame my first post.If you do download i hope you have fun coding and playing your server.
Lets start off with the credits... 90% Figment for the great base. 10% Me for making it blank almost and changing some stuff and adding stuff.
Heres a pretty blank source.
Custom admin zone + added by me [img]http://i730.photobucket.com/albums/ww305/haydog35/lol.jpg[/img] New shops added by me. [img]http://i730.photobucket.com/albums/ww305/haydog35/penisa.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i730.photobucket.com/albums/ww305/haydog35/dumbo.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i730.photobucket.com/albums/ww305/haydog35/PEE.jpg[/img]

[img]http://i730.photobucket.com/albums/ww305/haydog35/doo.jpg[/img]
Hope you like it.
Heres the link. http://uppit.com/TK4G2M
If there is anything you think i can do to make it better post under. Thanks
I will make a v2 way way different with alot more stuff. And ill be sure to make other sources Thanks Hope u like it[left][/left]
